			<dl>
<dd><i>"Creationism" can also refer to <a href="/wiki/Creation_myth" title="Creation myth">creation myths</a>, or to a <a href="/wiki/Creationism_(soul)" title="Creationism (soul)">concept about the origin of the soul</a>. For the movement in Spanish literature, see <a href="/wiki/Creacionismo" title="Creacionismo">creacionismo</a>.</i></dd>
</dl>
